flowchart TB
  app[Applications] --> scan[SCAN / Services RAC]
  scan --> db1[DB Server 1]
  scan --> db2[DB Server 2]
  db1 --> gi[Grid Infrastructure / ASM]
  db2 --> gi
  gi --> fabric[Fabric privé RoCE ou InfiniBand]
  fabric --> cell1[Storage Cell 1]
  fabric --> cell2[Storage Cell 2]
  fabric --> cell3[Storage Cell N]
  cell1 --> flash[Flash Cache / Flash Log]
  cell1 --> disks[Physical Disks]
  support[AHF / Exachk / TFA / EM] -.observe.-> db1
  support -.observe.-> cell1
